HEADWORD: antidisestablishmentarianism
<hw>an`ti*dis`es*tab`lish*men*ta"ri*an*ism</hw>
<pr>(⟦acr⟧n*t⟦esl⟧*d⟦icr⟧s`⟦ecr⟧s*t⟦acr⟧b`l⟦icr⟧sh*m⟦eit⟧n*t⟦acir⟧r"⟦esl⟧*⟦acr⟧n*⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>,
